5) Custom Module Folder structure:

Custom module should be added in the app/conde directory

- etc
  - module.xml
  - di.xml
  - frontend/routes.xml
- registration.php 
- composer.json
  - Controller
  - Model 
  - Block
  - view 
    - frontend
    - adminhtml 

6) What is object manager ? 

Object manager is the responsible for initiating object in the magento application. 

7) What is factory class ? 

Object manager is the responsible for initiating object, magento prohits to use object manager directly. Factories are exception to this rule because they require object manger to objectmanager to initiate the magento models. 

When call the factory in constructor, obbject manager generate the factory class to initiate the object for the model. So no need to defined externally. 

