1) What are advantages you see in magento 2 than magento 1? 



Admin Naviagtion
----------------

Magento 2, It is simplified and modernized


Add To Cart
-----------

- Magent 1, When user click the 'add to cart' button, user will be redirected to cart page. If users like to add another product to cart, user should comes to the previous page. This will create negative impacts. 
- Magento 2, It is developed with Ajax, so page doesn't load and user can add more products to the cart without delay. 


File Upload:
------------

- Able to add the video to the product. Currently vimeo and youtube are supported in magento.















